      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Equipped with the M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) for lightning-fast shifts and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle body actuators, ensuring the high-revving internals remain robust. Finished in Interlagos Blue, this specimen offers a visceral driving experience with the mechanical integrity enthusiasts demand.",
