      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been meticulously maintained throughout my ownership. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish that shines beautifully in the sunlight, though you will find some minor, age-appropriate road wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a light surface scratch near the trunk handle. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard is pristine with no sun damage. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape\u2014the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and there are no warning lights on the dash. I have kept a detailed log of all services, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. It has been a smoke-free and pet-free environment, consistently garage-kept to preserve its integrity. This is a complete, honest car ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
